Class EFLabel

  • java.lang.Object
    • dev.eternalformula.api.ui.UIElement
      • dev.eternalformula.api.ui.elements.EFLabel

  • public class EFLabel
extends UIElement
    The EFLabel is a simple element. It does not have a skin, and it simply acts as a text field.
